translate chinese whitneyq5_8726d7a4:

    # wt "Currently, we are dating, but you are also dating other people, correct?"
    wt "目前，我们虽然在交往，但你也在和其他人约会，对吧？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:17
translate chinese whitneyq5_6dba6230:

    # pc "Yes."
    pc "是的。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:19
translate chinese whitneyq5_277d2541:

    # wt "I am reaching the point where I don't think I can abide that any longer."
    wt "我已经到了无法再容忍这种状况的地步了。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:20
translate chinese whitneyq5_a2a6fb65:

    # pc "What do you mean?"
    pc "你什么意思？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:22
translate chinese whitneyq5_19e078cc:

    # wt "Well, [pcname]. I really like you. I'm ready to get more serious about our relationship."
    wt "嗯，[pcname]。我真的很喜欢你。我准备让我们的关系更进一步。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:24
translate chinese whitneyq5_36623c8c:

    # wt "So, soon, I would like you to stop seeing those other people and become monogamous with me."
    wt "所以，希望你很快能停止和其他人约会，只和我保持专一的关系。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:25
translate chinese whitneyq5_8dcb7c09:

    # wt "I'm not interested in having an open relationship or involving other people in the bedroom."
    wt "我对开放式关系或让其他人参与我们的亲密关系不感兴趣。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:26
translate chinese whitneyq5_5156766b:

    # wt "I just want you and me."
    wt "我只想和你在一起。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:28
translate chinese whitneyq5_43700f9c:

    # wt "Is this something that you want too?"
    wt "这也是你想要的吗？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:29
translate chinese whitneyq5_fd6b344e:

    # pc "Well, yeah... probably. I haven't fully decided yet."
    pc "嗯，是啊……大概吧。我还没完全想好。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:31
translate chinese whitneyq5_324949f9:

    # wt "I see."
    wt "我明白了。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:32
translate chinese whitneyq5_ff38597c:

    # wt "I don't expect a decision immediately... but soon."
    wt "我不指望你立刻做决定……但希望尽快。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:34
translate chinese whitneyq5_87af29c5:

    # wt "After graduation, maybe? You will be finishing school and moving into a career."
    wt "毕业之后，怎么样？你即将完成学业，开始职业生涯。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:36
translate chinese whitneyq5_ac897f1d:

    # wt "You are welcome to come work for me in the lab, of course."
    wt "当然，你随时可以来我的实验室工作。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:37
translate chinese whitneyq5_ede37c91:

    # wt "I could use the extra hands and I can pay well. You're capable enough."
    wt "我正缺人手，薪水也很丰厚。你完全胜任。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:39
translate chinese whitneyq5_047d2aa0:

    # wt "But I hoped that you might move in as well."
    wt "但我希望你能搬进来住。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:40
translate chinese whitneyq5_f2d0fed6:

    # wt "We could take a step forward with our relationship... maybe even get married?"
    wt "我们可以把关系更进一步……甚至结婚？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:42
translate chinese whitneyq5_318271a9:

    # wt "Is that something that you'd be interested in?"
    wt "你对这种事有兴趣吗？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:43
translate chinese whitneyq5_ba2f3d67:

    # pc "Yeah, maybe."
    pc "嗯，也许吧。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:45
translate chinese whitneyq5_07539fdb:

    # wt "Right. Maybe. But you'll decide after graduation?"
    wt "是啊。也许吧。但你要等到毕业后再决定？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:46
translate chinese whitneyq5_323862b8:

    # pc "Yeah, I think that's enough time. I'll decide."
    pc "是的，我觉得时间还够。我会决定的。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:48
translate chinese whitneyq5_9bbeb9a1:

    # wt "Good. I can deal with you seeing other people until then."
    wt "好。在那之前，我能接受你和其他人约会。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq5.rpy:50
translate chinese whitneyq5_78f521c5:

    # wt "But I am looking forward to having you all to myself."
    wt "但我很期待能独占你。"

